---
---

<section id="information" class="info-section">
  <div class="info-inner">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="info-header">
      <p class="section-label">Know Before You Go</p>
      <h2 class="info-title">
        <span class="text-gradient-cyan-magenta">Information</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="info-subtitle">Everything you need to prepare for the journey.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid of info cards -->
    <div class="info-grid">

      <!-- Getting There -->
      <div class="card-glass info-card">
        <div class="card-icon">📍</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Getting There</h3>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li>Desert Oasis, Shitim — off Route 90, southern Dead Sea region</li>
          <li>GPS coordinates will be sent via email 72 hrs before the event</li>
          <li>Carpooling board available in the attendee WhatsApp group</li>
          <li>Nearest town: Ein Bokek (~25 km north)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Dates & Times -->
      <div class="card-glass info-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🗓</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Dates & Times</h3>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li><strong>Gates open:</strong> Sep 17, 2026 at 14:00</li>
          <li><strong>Music starts:</strong> Sep 17 at 17:00</li>
          <li><strong>Music ends:</strong> Sep 19 at ~13:00</li>
          <li><strong>Site closes:</strong> Sep 19 at 16:00</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Camping -->
      <div class="card-glass info-card">
        <div class="card-icon">⛺</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Camping</h3>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li>Free camping included with every ticket</li>
          <li>Designated camping zones marked on the site map</li>
          <li>No fires — bring warm layers for desert nights (can drop to 18°C)</li>
          <li>Shade structures recommended — daytime heat 35–40°C</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- What to Bring -->
      <div class="card-glass info-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🎒</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">What to Bring</h3>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li>Plenty of water (minimum 4L/day per person)</li>
          <li>Sun protection: hat, sunscreen SPF 50+, long sleeves</li>
          <li>Tent, sleeping bag, and ground mat</li>
          <li>Headlamp, earplugs, and personal medication</li>
          <li>Cash — the site is card-free</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- On-Site -->
      <div class="card-glass info-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🌵</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">On-Site</h3>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li>Food & drink vendors open throughout the event</li>
          <li>Chill-out area with hammocks and shade near the stage</li>
          <li>Medical station staffed 24/7</li>
          <li>Safe space tent for mental health support</li>
          <li>No generators — silence outside the stage zone after 07:00</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Rules & Etiquette -->
      <div class="card-glass info-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🤝</div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Rules & Etiquette</h3>
        <ul class="card-list">
          <li>Leave no trace — pack out everything you bring in</li>
          <li>Respect the desert ecosystem — stay on marked paths</li>
          <li>Photography: always ask before shooting people</li>
          <li>Zero tolerance for harassment of any kind</li>
          <li>Sound complaints to event staff, not to neighbors</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>


  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .info-section {
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .info-inner {
    max-width: 80rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .info-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .info-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .info-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    max-width: 32rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .info-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .info-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }
  .info-card {
    padding: 1.75rem;
  }
  .card-icon {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-cyan-neon);
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .card-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .card-list li {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .card-list li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-cyan-neon);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .card-list strong {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
